    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound 996.2-generation Carrera, featuring the refined 3.6L M96 flat-six engine and a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. This naturally aspirated powerhouse benefits from VarioCam Plus technology, providing a broad torque curve and a visceral 7,300 RPM redline. The drivetrain has been significantly fortified with a documented LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh rear main seal, addressing critical longevity concerns. The chassis maintains excellent torsional rigidity, complemented by a factory-optioned limited-slip differential for superior power delivery through the apex. Recent service includes a full cooling system flush and new ignition coils. This is a driver-spec 911 that offers pure hydraulic steering feedback and a chassis tuned for the enthusiast who values mechanical transparency.",
